pageProduct.name: VitalStrength Pre Workout Shot Arctic Blue 5 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

On-the-go Pre-Workout Gel. No water or mixing just a convenient shot of energy & focus. Vital Strength’s Pre-Workout shots feature innovative design that means you can take them anywhere, anytime. Easy to use & specially formulated to increase energy, focus & strength.

Our concentrated formula is loaded with nitric oxide boosters, big L-citrulline and Beta-alanine for increased energy production, muscle strength, power & endurance. Carefully selected stimulants give you intense pumps pushing you to train harder, for longer. Convenient & easy to transport these Pre-Workout shots are perfect for any occasion.

• Convenient easy to use gel shot, consumer anywhere anytime
• No water or missing required.
• 1.5g Nitric Oxide AAKG increased blood flow to muscle & tissues
• 1g Beta Alanine to aid muscular endurance
• 2.5g L-Citrulline boosts blood flow
• 200mg of caffeine for explosive energy
• 860mg Taurine per serve enhances athletic capacity.
• Improves physical performance
• Delays mental fatigue
• Promotes clarity throughout entire workout

Warnings

 THIS PRODUCT SHOULD BE USED IN CONJUNCTION WITH AN APPROPRIATE PHYSICAL TRAINING OR EXERCISE PROGRAM. THIS PRODUCT IS NOT A SOLE SOURCE OF NUTRITION AND SHOULD BE CONSUMED IN CONJUNCTION WITH A NUTRITIOUS DIET AND APPROPRIATE FLUID INTAKE. NOT SUITABLE FOR CHILDREN UNDER 15 YEARS OR PREGNANT WOMEN. SHOULD ONLY BE USED UNDER MEDICAL OR DIETETIC SUPERVISION. EXCEEDING THE RECOMMENDED SERVING SIZE MAY CAUSE HARM DUE TO THE HIGH LEVELS CAFFEINE AND OTHER NUTRIENTS. CONTAINS CAFFEINE: NOT RECOMMENDED FOR CHILDREN, PREGNANT OR LACTATING WOMEN INDIVIDUALS SENSITIVE TO CAFFEINE.

Common Uses

Take Pre-Workout Gel Shots prior to training to increase motivation, boost energy & endurance.

Ingredients

Maltodextrin, Citric acid, Flavours, Ascorbic acid, Carboxylmethylcellulose, Silicon dioxide, Sucralose, Acesulphame Potassium, Colour, Guar Gum, Xanthan Gum, Potassium Sorbate, Water. Soy Lecithin. Contains: Soy.

Directions

Consume 1 shot to assess tolerance, progress to 2 shots if required. Do not exceed two shots per day.
